channel.title: Your future job?
channel.description: What are your plans for the future? What I have four possible options that fit my tastes. For one, I always wanted to be an Artist, simply because it requires no diploma or education. But, your only make as much money as you sell your art and it's value. Two, neurosurgeon because the brain and its layout fascinates me, and I'm sorta interested in finding out more. Three, I wish to become a Physicist, mainly theoretical physics interest me the most. Quantum Mechanics is also good as well. Finally Fourth, I want to get my bachelors degree, then my masters, and finally start my own business.
